          "id": "s2_p1_a_q1",
          "nodeType": "QUESTION",
          "parentId": "s2_p1_a",
          "orderIndex": 2,
          "label": null,
          "maxPoints": 2,
          "topicCodes": [],
          "blocks": [
            {
              "id": "s2_p1_a_q1_prompt_1",
              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1-Are the following statements true or false? Justify the false ones.\na) The name Mesopotamia refers to an ancient civilization.\nb) The land of Mesopotamia is made fertile by the Tigris and Euphrates Rivers.\nc) The Sumerians invented a new form of writing.\nd) The cuneiform writing lasted a few years only."
            },
            {
              "id": "s2_p1_a_q1_solution_2",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "1.\na. false : it refers to a geographical region\nb. true\nc. true\nd. false: It lasted over 2000 years"
            },
            {
